    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/c9aa6c538bb9c1791fc890fe3378f7dd.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/c9aa6c538bb9c1791fc890fe3378f7dd.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《动物摇滚团》是一款摇滚乐队管理类角色扮演游戏，其背景为平行时空中上世纪 90 年代的美国。 本作剧本由 《巫师 3》与《赛博朋克 2077》的主创编剧亲自操刀，配音阵容包括《博德之门 3》声优及摇滚传奇人物伊基・ 波普。这款悲喜剧风格的游戏，将带玩家直击音乐行业残酷的幕后真相。 你的每个 抉择，都将决定乐队从车库无名之辈到巨星的成长轨迹——是坚守创作自由，还是 沦为商业化傀儡？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/3f8b6b4aec86ace8bcad9d969bb3dd75.avif?t=1771253718\" width=1560 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/997ddda19bd6e55699130bdb53b5d5b0.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/997ddda19bd6e55699130bdb53b5d5b0.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/997ddda19bd6e55699130bdb53b5d5b0.mp4?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《动物摇滚团》呈现了一个兼具情感张力与黑色幽默的故事，所有情节通过实操推进。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家绝非旁观者，而是乐队成长的亲历者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你需要完成各类关键任务、合理规划资金，还要小心平衡乐队成员们脆弱的心态——这些不仅关乎乐队的成败， 甚至决定着他们能否继续坚持下去。 同时，你得编排演出曲目、演出前检修设备，还需亲自参与 节奏型舞台演出。 游戏中没有轻松躺赢的可能，你的行动 直接推动剧情，成败皆由自身决策决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/bc9352fde7fdf0d81e9d8b003ed9d32f.avif?t=1771253718\" width=1560 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/adc530dbf1dd74ff9d126bb36e3347b4.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/adc530dbf1dd74ff9d126bb36e3347b4.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/adc530dbf1dd74ff9d126bb36e3347b4.mp4?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在音乐行业的道德困境中周旋，与唱片公司谈判，在坚守创作初心 与妥协让步之间做选择，还要在艺术本真和商业压力间寻找平衡。 从态度冷漠的场地老板、 演出推广人，到冷酷无情的唱片公司高管，你与这些人的相处方式、签订的每一份合约， 以及坚守或突破的底线，都将共同书写这支乐队的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/896382eee3c7f4ff11cd68f9641dca6f.avif?t=1771253718\" width=1560 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/3a95a7635093b2b25a01263a78b8a670.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/3a95a7635093b2b25a01263a78b8a670.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/3a95a7635093b2b25a01263a78b8a670.mp4?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你得妥善管理乐队资源以维持正常运转： 用有限的资金安排成员的饮食、 维修损坏的乐器设备，还有预订排练场地。 既要让乐队成员保持基本的理智以维持团队稳定， 又要保留那份支撑摇滚创作的狂放与不羁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/75b87d18d332b01c496fb92b03b243de.avif?t=1771253718\" width=1560 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/cc341c61de6ab118ab141622bb549783.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/cc341c61de6ab118ab141622bb549783.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/cc341c61de6ab118ab141622bb549783.mp4?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想证明乐队的实力，就得做好演出的全流程筹备：挑选能凸显成员优势的曲目组合、搭配契合乐队风格的 演出设备，再完美完成充满动感的节奏型舞台表演。 演出成功会收获丰厚报酬 与大量粉丝； 一旦失利，不仅乐队声誉受损，成员也会士气大挫。 掌控舞台，机遇 自来。 一旦失手，机遇不再。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/f0d4356f005615f5ecc6950c2b31e0cc.avif?t=1771253718\" width=1560 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/7fb94fc620caf9f497ebd631a00bbb7f.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/7fb94fc620caf9f497ebd631a00bbb7f.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/7fb94fc620caf9f497ebd631a00bbb7f.mp4?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于精心构建的平行时空美国。在这里，垃圾摇滚、狂热资本与 MTV  在此交织碰撞。 游戏采用手绘美术风格，完美还原了成熟动画的质感， 让众多标志性场景栩栩如生：既有传奇演出场馆、廉价小酒吧，也有唱片店、电台， 还有孕育摇滚文化的破旧街区。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内包含 17 首原创全长曲目，精准复刻了 90 年代另类摇滚的音乐风格，玩家不仅能 聆听经典的西雅图摇滚曲风，还能在游戏演出中亲自演绎这些歌曲。 这里没有刻意的怀旧情怀，而是 构建了一个有血有肉的世界，让玩家能真切感受到那个年代的独特魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/4630d2e027955a175a8837f442fd36f2.avif?t=1771253718\" width=1560 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/04adf2c8ff7925d4d10f7e4bdfd9f151.poster.avif?t=1771253718\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/04adf2c8ff7925d4d10f7e4bdfd9f151.webm?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445880/extras/04adf2c8ff7925d4d10f7e4bdfd9f151.mp4?t=1771253718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为经理，你每天都要面对层出不穷的麻烦：成员间的矛盾冲突、演出设备突发故障，以及行业的种种桎梏， 它们日复一日地消磨着乐队的创作灵感。 你能否将车库里杂乱的演奏声，打造成影响一个时代的经典金曲？ 又或者，这支乐队最终会沦为 天赋被浪费的反面教材？ 音乐本可以改变世界，但前提是这支乐队能坚持到 被大众听见的那一天。 而此刻，才刚到周一而已。</p>",
